anilla Tweaks features including \"Smoother Font\"<br>Changes most Vanilla textures.</strong><strong><br>50+ Mods supported<br>Animated Textures<br><br></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Vanilla Screenshots<br></strong></h2>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img style=\"font-weight: 400;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/636912/description_2b35af2d-d04c-4cc2-99dc-ee27693f33fa.png\"><img style=\"font-weight: 400;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/636912/description_fbb375c3-728c-4e0d-8726-2b8946915b80.jpg\"><img style=\"font-weight: 400;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/636912/description_94e851d2-da6d-427f-8955-b63337c7422f.jpg\"><img style=\"font-weight: 400;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/636912/description_253d48d8-2c56-455a-b77b-d60b3298ed6f.jpg\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/636912/description_87da7080-bf42-404d-b7e2-e9807001bfac.jpg\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/636912/description_c0efcfc0-0222-4149-a9ec-fedb8d41719a.jpg\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/636912/description_e8f5c436-2878-473b-bf36-ce7a7048cfe3.jpg\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/636912/description_fe71bc7e-6497-4f2b-b4b9-debf7b51d792.jpg\"><br>Taken in-game using&nbsp; -&gt; AON-Dark UI Overhaul-1.21.x-v4.0.zip</p>\n</div>\n<h2><strong><br>Modded Screenshots<br></strong></h2>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/636912/description_24bf1627-b134-4ff6-bceb-686ac8f2578e.jpg\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/636912/description_73705b3f-2901-4ca6-bf39-dc7f6a5aa53a.jpg\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/636912/description_c578a8f3-dbf6-4b85-9820-f598267a9476.jpg\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/636912/description_d